{
  "article_id": "McDougall1890",
  "paragraphs": [
    [
      {
        "text": "May 1, Tuesday Morning. — This is the day we are to bid adieu to"
      },
      {
        "text": "San Francisco",
        "entity_key": "ci_sf",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "and, with the exception of leaving"
      },
      {
        "text": "my husband",
        "entity_key": "wmcd",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "[then absent, I believe, at the mines] and three or four friends, I confess I leave it without regret."
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "The morning is very gloomy and unpleasant. We left Mr. Bawden's house at half past nine o'clock and walked down to the point,"
      },
      {
        "text": "Colonel John Stevenson",
        "entity_key": "jstev",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "and"
      },
      {
        "text": "Doctor Parker",
        "entity_key": "wpa",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "overtaking us on the way."
      },
      {
        "text": "Mr.",
        "entity_key": "owh",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "and"
      },
      {
        "text": "Mrs. Wheeler",
        "entity_key": "mwhe",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": ","
      },
      {
        "text": "Mrs. Goodwin",
        "entity_key": "mgo",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": ","
      },
      {
        "text": "Captain Folsom",
        "entity_key": "jfol",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": ", and"
      },
      {
        "text": "Mr.",
        "entity_key": "gri",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "and"
      },
      {
        "text": "Mrs. Grimes",
        "entity_key": "mgr",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "came down to"
      },
      {
        "text": "the steamer",
        "entity_key": "sh_california",
        "entity_type": "ship"
      },
      {
        "text": "soon afterward. We sat and talked some time, — made merry, or tried to, but many were the sad hearts. Friends were parting, perhaps forever; some with a long and dangerous journey before them, and others . . . . where comforts cannot be procured even for gold."
      },
      {
        "text": "Mr.",
        "entity_key": "baw",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "and"
      },
      {
        "text": "Mrs. Bawden",
        "entity_key": "mbaw",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": ","
      },
      {
        "text": "Colonel Stevenson",
        "entity_key": "jstev",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": ","
      },
      {
        "text": "Doctor Parker",
        "entity_key": "wpa",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": ", and myself embarked on"
      },
      {
        "text": "a whale boat",
        "entity_key": "sh_whaleboat",
        "entity_type": "ship"
      },
      {
        "text": "for"
      },
      {
        "text": "the steamer",
        "entity_key": "sh_california",
        "entity_type": "ship"
      },
      {
        "text": "at half past ten. Found"
      },
      {
        "text": "the California",
        "entity_key": "sh_california",
        "entity_type": "ship"
      },
      {
        "text": "as cold and cheerless as ever, though much cleaner than on her trip up."
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "At two o'clock we left"
      },
      {
        "text": "San Francisco",
        "entity_key": "ci_sf",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "for"
      },
      {
        "text": "Saucelito",
        "entity_key": "ci_sa",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": ", where we have lain ever since, getting on water. Had a very poor dinner of roast beef and yams about three o'clock. I regretted very much leaving"
      },
      {
        "text": "Mr. Bawden",
        "entity_key": "baw",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": ","
      },
      {
        "text": "the Colonel",
        "entity_key": "jstev",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": ", and"
      },
      {
        "text": "the Doctor",
        "entity_key": "wpa",
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": ", who have shown me great kindness since I have been in"
      },
      {
        "text": "California",
        "entity_key": "st_cal",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": ";"
      },
      {
        "text": "the two latter",
        "entity_keys": [
          "jstev",
          "wpa"
        ],
        "entity_type": "person"
      },
      {
        "text": "seem more like brothers than anything else."
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "Saucelito",
        "entity_key": "ci_sa",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "is a little cove in among the hills, a very picturesque place although the hills are barren of trees. Very fine water here, and easy of access for vessels."
      }
    ],
    [
      {
        "text": "Eight o'clock. — We are just done tea, and being tired, cold, and low-spirited, I determined to go to bed, hoping to waken tomorrow morning in the"
      },
      {
        "text": "Bay of Monterey",
        "entity_key": "re_mobay",
        "entity_type": "place"
      },
      {
        "text": "."
      }
    ]
  ]
}